  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">This Ethics and Compliance Charter supplements the Seller Terms &amp; Conditions (“Seller T&amp;Cs”) and the Quality Charter. In the event of a conflict, the provisions of the Seller T&amp;Cs will prevail on both charters. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.295;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">All terms starting with a capital letter have the meaning given to such terms in the Seller T&amp;Cs, accepted by the Seller. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.295;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Any Seller who wishes to sell Products on the Back Market Platform undertakes to comply with the principles set out in this Charter. In the event of a violation of this Charter, Back Market reserves its right to suspend or close the Seller Account as stated in the Seller T&amp;Cs, which will prevent the Seller from using the Platform, without prejudice to the other penalties that Back Market may seek or that may be pronounced against the Seller. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.295;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">This Charter may change and you will be informed of any amendments by email or by any other digital means (such as Back Office notifications) sent by Back Market at least one month before such amendments take effect. You are free to accept the amended charter and undertake to comply with the updated Charter or to discontinue using the Platform in accordance with the Seller T&amp;Cs. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001;\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.295;text-indent: -0.15pt;text-align: center;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.15pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Have questions about this Ethics and Compliance Charter? </span></span></span></span></span><br><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Reach out to:</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\"> </span></span></span></span></span><a href=\"mailto:legal-sellers@backmarket.com\" style=\"text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #1155cc;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">legal-sellers@backmarket.com</span></span></span></span></span></span></a></span></p>\n \n\n<h3 style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.2pt;text-align: center;margin-top: 32px;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.2pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Part 1. The 10 Principles of the United Nations </span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 20pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Global Compact </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h3>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">In the interest of improving our approach to social responsibility, Back Market has committed to, and asks Sellers to commit themselves to respecting the following 10 principles established by the UN Global Compact regarding human rights, international labor laws, the environment, and the fight against corruption: </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<div>\n<table style=\"border: none;border-collapse: collapse;\" width=\"637\"><colgroup><col width=\"637\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;vertical-align: top;background-color: #0a2d61;padding: 7px 8px 7px 8px;border-top: 1px solid #000000;border-right: 1px solid #000000;border-left: 1px solid #000000;width: 637px;\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: center;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"overflow: hidden;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #e2f77e;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Human Rights</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">Principle 1</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">:</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\"> </span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Sellers should support and respect the protection of internationally proclaimed human rights.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">Principle 2</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">: </span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Sellers should make sure they are not accomplices to human rights abuses.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<div>\n<table style=\"border: none;border-collapse: collapse;\" width=\"637\"><colgroup><col width=\"637\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;vertical-align: top;background-color: #0a2d61;padding: 7px 8px 7px 8px;border-top: 1px solid #000000;border-right: 1px solid #000000;border-left: 1px solid #000000;width: 637px;\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: center;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"overflow: hidden;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #e2f77e;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">International labor standards </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">Principle 3</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">:</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\"> </span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Sellers should uphold the freedom of association and the effective recognition of the right to collective bargaining.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">Principle 4</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">:</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\"> </span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Sellers should uphold the elimination of all forms of forced and compulsory labor.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">Principle 5</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">:</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\"> </span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Sellers should uphold the effective abolition of child labor.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">Principle 6</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">:</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\"> Sellers should uphold the elimination of discrimination in respect of employment and occupation.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<div>\n<table style=\"border: none;border-collapse: collapse;\" width=\"637\"><colgroup><col width=\"637\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;vertical-align: top;background-color: #0a2d61;padding: 7px 8px 7px 8px;border-top: 1px solid #000000;border-right: 1px solid #000000;border-left: 1px solid #000000;width: 637px;\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: center;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"overflow: hidden;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #e2f77e;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">The environment</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">Principle 7</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">: </span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Sellers should support a precautionary approach to environmental challenges.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">Principle 8</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">: </span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Sellers should undertake initiatives to promote greater environmental responsibility.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">Principle 9</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">:</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\"> Sellers should encourage the development and diffusion of environmentally friendly technologies.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<div>\n<table style=\"border: none;border-collapse: collapse;\" width=\"637\"><colgroup><col width=\"637\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;vertical-align: top;background-color: #0a2d61;padding: 7px 8px 7px 8px;border-top: 1px solid #000000;border-right: 1px solid #000000;border-left: 1px solid #000000;width: 637px;\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: center;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"overflow: hidden;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #e2f77e;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Fighting against corruption</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"text-decoration-skip-ink: none;\">Principle 10</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">:</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\"> </span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Sellers should work against corruption in all of its forms, including extortion and bribery (see part 2 of this Charter for more on corruption).</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<h3 style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-align: center;margin-top: 32px;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Part 2. Anti-corruption</span></span></span></span></span><br><span style=\"font-size: 20pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">and anti-money laundering </span></span></span></span></span></span></h3>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Back Market pays special attention to the fight against fraud, corruption, influence peddling, and money laundering, and asks Sellers to commit to respecting the principles described below. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<div>\n<table style=\"border: none;border-collapse: collapse;\" width=\"637\"><colgroup><col width=\"637\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid #000000;vertical-align: top;background-color: #0a2d61;padding: 7px 8px 7px 8px;border-top: 1px solid #000000;border-right: 1px solid #000000;border-left: 1px solid #000000;width: 637px;\">\n\t\t\t<p style=\"line-height: 1.2;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: center;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"overflow: hidden;\"><span style=\"overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #e2f77e;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Sellers’ Commitments</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\t\t\t</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">The Seller undertakes, both with regards to themselves, their employees, agents, representatives, shareholders, members, and persons acting on their behalf, that they will conduct their business in strict compliance with all applicable local and international laws and regulations on corruption, money laundering, and terrorism (hereinafter, the “Regulations”). </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n \n\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001;text-indent: -0.1pt;text-align: justify;padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0.1pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">In particular, the Seller will not engage in the following practices:</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul><li style=\"list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Corrupt practices </span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">meant to promote or give a direct or indirect advantage to any individual or legal entity (whether a public or private person) for the purpose of carrying out, or abstaining from carrying out, an act that falls within their duties ;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li></ul>\n\n<ul><li style=\"list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Money laundering practices </span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">meant to conceal the origin of property or revenue of the perpetrator of a crime or offense or to help in the placement, concealment, or conversion of a transaction with respect to the direct or indirect proceeds of a crime or offense ;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li></ul>\n\n<ul><li style=\"list-style-type: disc;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">Deceptive or unfair practices</span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\"> </span></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt;font-variant: normal;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span style=\"color: #0a1740;\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 300;\"><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">meant to deliberately deceive, intentionally conceal facts, or avoid legal or regulatory obligations, for the purpose of obtaining an illegitimate benefit.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li></ul>\n\n<p> </p>"
}